<t>
<field>DEFAULT.TARGET</field>
<desc>
            <p>PW.ACTIVITY.OBJECT</p>
            <p />
            <p> DEFAULT.TARGET</p>
            <p />
            <p> It can be used as Target field when executing a PW.ACTIVITY record. </p>
            <p> If a target field value has been entered in this field, then this value will be defaulted in the field TARGET when trying to create a new Activity in PW.ACTIVITY.</p>
            <p />
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p />
            <p> Up to 35 alphanumeric characters</p>
            <p> Same syntax to be used as      that is used at the T24 command line. APPLICATION/VERSION/EB.TABLE.DEFINITION      Function Record</p>
            <p> E.g. ACCOUNT, I F3</p>
            <p />
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>DEFAULT.TRAGET</field>
<desc>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p> PW.ACTIVITY.OBJECT</p>
            <p />
            <p> DEFAULT.TARGET</p>
            <p> At a later date can be used as Target field when executing a PW.ACTIVITY record. If a target field has not been entered in the PW.ACTIVITY record this DEFAULT.TARGET field will be used to execute an activity. </p>
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p />
            <p> Up to 35 alphanumeric      characters.</p>
            <p> Same syntax to be used as      that is used at the T24 command line. APPLICATION/VERSION/EB.TABLE.DEFINITION      Function Record</p>
            <p> EG. ACCOUNT, I F3</p>
        </desc>
</t>
