<t>
<field>PW.ACTIVITY.OBJECT.ID</field>
<desc>
            <p />
            <p> PW.ACTIVITY.OBJECT</p>
            <p />
            <p> @ID</p>
            <p> Descriptive key used for naming convention of the PW.ACTIVITY records. This key will is used to concatenate with a PW.VERB key to create the PW.ACTIVITY key. </p>
            <p> It is suggested that this key describes the PW.ACIVITY to be run.</p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p />
            <p> EG.</p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p> Where PW.ACTIVITY.OBJECT</p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p />
            <p> And </p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p />
            <p />
            <p> The PW.ACTIVITY key would = &amp;#8216;CREATE.ACCOUNT&amp;#8217;</p>
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p />
            <p> Up to 35 alphanumeric      characters.</p>
        </desc>
